  "text": "Mutation signatures. Mutation signatures were calculated using the decon-structSigs R package [CITATION_1] . The signatures evaluated were the 30 COSMIC signatures for mutational processes in human cancers (http://cancer.sanger.ac.uk/cosmic/ signatures). A difference of indel counts between limited and extensive stage samples (Supplementary table 1) was tested by unpaired t-test.",
